      "author": "goryugocast",
      "description": "## 0.1.8\n\nBot-clean lint pass. No user-facing behavior changes beyond the items below.\n\n### Changed\n- Summary view tab title: `LLR Summary` → `Daily summary` (sentence-case compliance for community plugin lint).\n- Notice text capitalization adjusted: \"Daily Notes\" → \"Daily notes\" / \"daily notes\" in two notices.\n\n### Internal\n- Aligned local eslint config with the obsidian-releases bot ruleset (`no-explicit-any`, `await-thenable`, `no-floating-promises`, `no-unnecessary-type-assertion`, `no-console`, `eslint-comments/require-description`).\n- Replaced all `as any` Obsidian internal API casts with narrow structural type aliases (`AppInternal`, `WorkspaceInternal`, `CM6View`, etc.).\n- Removed unused imports / variables.\n- TypeScript `tsc --noEmit` now passes cleanly (added `ES2021` lib, `allowSyntheticDefaultImports`, `skipLibCheck`).\n\n### Notes\n- 0.1.7 release artifacts were rejected by bot due to missing rule coverage. 0.1.8 supersedes.\n",
