      "author": "goryugocast",
      "description": "First public release of LLR: Live Life Recording system.\n\nHighlights:\n- Record task start, finish, and elapsed time directly in Markdown checkboxes.\n- Use a single `Toggle Task` command to create, start, and finish tasks.\n- Insert and manage repeating routines in daily notes.\n- Review the day from the Summary View sidebar.\n- Keep all task data as plain text in your vault.\n\nInstall:\n- Use BRAT and add `goryugocast/llr` as a beta plugin.\n",
